1
00:00:03,254 --> 00:00:05,507
<i>Within the spreading darkness</i>

2
00:00:05,590 --> 00:00:08,218
<i>I pledged a vow to the revolution</i>

3
00:00:08,343 --> 00:00:13,348
<i>I can't let anybody interrupt it</i>

4
00:00:13,431 --> 00:00:18,520
<i>I'm going to change</i>

5
00:00:26,986 --> 00:00:31,282
<i>The future that
the forbidden fruit foretells...</i>

6
00:00:31,366 --> 00:00:35,245
<i>I'm going to change</i>

7
00:00:35,328 --> 00:00:39,707
<i>The dream into reality</i>

8
00:00:42,293 --> 00:00:48,341
<i>The ending</i>

9
00:00:48,424 --> 00:00:51,594
<i>That everybody wants</i>

10
00:00:52,554 --> 00:00:54,847
<i>Within the spreading darkness</i>

11
00:00:54,931 --> 00:00:57,600
<i>I pledged our vow to the revolution</i>

12
00:00:57,684 --> 00:01:02,480
<i>I can't let anybody interrupt it</i>

13
00:01:02,647 --> 00:01:07,902
<i>Someday I'll show you</i>

14
00:01:07,986 --> 00:01:11,322
<i>The bright and ideal</i>

15
00:01:11,406 --> 00:01:17,287
<i>World</i>

16
00:01:26,879 --> 00:01:31,884
Because you're
my very first friend...

17
00:01:36,222 --> 00:01:37,724
- Misa.
- Yes?

18
00:01:37,974 --> 00:01:41,144
Could you ask Rem to kill L?

19
00:01:42,604 --> 00:01:43,646
Rem...

20
00:01:44,147 --> 00:01:45,481
I want Light to love me.

21
00:01:45,982 --> 00:01:48,026
Light and I will be grateful.
That would be my happiness.

22
00:01:50,695 --> 00:01:53,990
Fine. I'll kill L for you.

23
00:01:54,907 --> 00:01:56,159
<i>I will die,</i>

24
00:01:57,201 --> 00:01:58,411
<i>this easily?</i>

25
00:01:59,621 --> 00:02:02,624
WAGER

26
00:02:03,458 --> 00:02:04,834
So when should I kill him?

27
00:02:05,877 --> 00:02:09,422
If you take me to wherever he is,
I can kill him immediately.

28
00:02:10,298 --> 00:02:11,382
It should be done
as soon as possible.

29
00:02:12,050 --> 00:02:13,092
Tomorrow if you can.

30
00:02:13,593 --> 00:02:16,387
But it's still too soon to
make a decision now...

31
00:02:17,930 --> 00:02:21,434
I'll give you an answer after
I think of a way to kill him tonight.

32
00:02:22,018 --> 00:02:23,019
All right.

33
00:02:23,561 --> 00:02:27,607
No matter what,
don't kill him until I say so, got it.

34
00:02:28,274 --> 00:02:29,609
No matter what! Got it?

35
00:02:30,234 --> 00:02:32,737
All right, I promise...

36
00:02:33,529 --> 00:02:34,989
Only in regard to L.

37
00:02:36,032 --> 00:02:38,660
Misa, give me
your cell phone number.

38
00:02:38,868 --> 00:02:42,121
It's about time!
Give me yours too, Light!

39
00:02:42,747 --> 00:02:44,874
No, I can't give you mine.

40
00:02:45,208 --> 00:02:48,461
Why not?! We're lovers!

41
00:02:49,045 --> 00:02:51,798
I told you,
I'm under police surveillance.

42
00:02:52,298 --> 00:02:56,135
The police now can listen in
on phone conversations.

43
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:00,973
In that case, here.

44
00:03:01,099 --> 00:03:02,809
I'll give you one of
my own cell phones.

45
00:03:03,101 --> 00:03:05,770
I just ended up with three after
getting them for different jobs...

46
00:03:06,562 --> 00:03:07,563
That's a good idea.

47
00:03:07,939 --> 00:03:09,607
Using your phone would
probably be all right.

48
00:03:09,691 --> 00:03:10,692
All right!

49
00:03:11,025 --> 00:03:12,694
I'll call you every day.

50
00:03:12,777 --> 00:03:13,986
I'll also send you a lot of texts!

51
00:03:14,570 --> 00:03:16,197
No, I'll be keeping it off.

52
00:03:16,489 --> 00:03:19,033
I'll be the only one
making calls,

53
00:03:19,117 --> 00:03:20,368
and I'll only tell you what
you need to know.

54
00:03:20,702 --> 00:03:22,370
What? No way...

55
00:03:23,287 --> 00:03:24,789
When are you going to call?

56
00:03:25,456 --> 00:03:26,666
Probably tomorrow...

57
00:03:27,417 --> 00:03:31,129
I'll call once even if I decide
not to execute L.

58
00:03:31,796 --> 00:03:32,880
What? Tomorrow?

59
00:03:33,423 --> 00:03:35,842
It doesn't sound like something
a boyfriend would call about,

60
00:03:35,925 --> 00:03:37,593
but we can talk
about love afterwards.

61
00:03:37,802 --> 00:03:40,221
Well Misa,
go home for today.

62
00:03:40,513 --> 00:03:42,974
What? Why? It's only 7:00.

63
00:03:43,141 --> 00:03:45,017
The time for love
has just begun, hasn't it?

64
00:03:45,393 --> 00:03:47,645
We can go get dinner,
look at the night sky,

65
00:03:47,729 --> 00:03:50,314
and after that, the main event...

66
00:03:51,065 --> 00:03:52,191
Misa.

67
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:03,995
Got it?

68
00:04:04,495 --> 00:04:05,663
Go home for today.

69
00:04:06,664 --> 00:04:07,749
Yes...

70
00:04:08,207 --> 00:04:10,793
Also, when you're talking
outside with Rem,

71
00:04:11,002 --> 00:04:14,172
whisper and make sure that
no one's around.

72
00:04:14,839 --> 00:04:16,466
That's what Ryuk and I do.

73
00:04:16,883 --> 00:04:17,884
Yes...

74
00:04:18,176 --> 00:04:19,969
Thanks for having me over...

75
00:04:20,303 --> 00:04:23,181
Misa, come again tomorrow!

76
00:04:26,768 --> 00:04:29,187
That kiss was so sudden,
it surprised me.

77
00:04:29,687 --> 00:04:33,024
I need to keep
Misa deeply in love with me.

78
00:04:33,524 --> 00:04:34,567
Oh?

79
00:04:34,859 --> 00:04:37,695
Besides that, I need to decide
if I should kill L tomorrow or not.

80
00:04:38,362 --> 00:04:41,574
I hasn't made himself public yet.
So if Ryuga dies...

81
00:04:41,741 --> 00:04:46,287
I have to be prepared to become
an even greater suspect...

82
00:04:46,579 --> 00:04:47,622
I see.

83
00:04:48,122 --> 00:04:49,999
I thought you were hesitating

84
00:04:50,374 --> 00:04:52,877
because he said that
you were his friend.

85
00:04:53,377 --> 00:04:56,339
Friend? I was just playing along.

86
00:04:56,881 --> 00:05:00,134
From the beginning, I've said
that if it's friendship he wants,

87
00:05:00,218 --> 00:05:01,385
then I'll give it.

88
00:05:01,928 --> 00:05:06,682
Ryuga is Light Yagami's friend,
on the surface... But L is Kira's enemy.

89
00:05:16,025 --> 00:05:18,236
<i>Yes, L is my enemy...</i>

90
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:21,948
<i>Since Ryuga's revealed that he's L,
I must kill him...</i>

91
00:05:22,907 --> 00:05:24,784
<i>If L dies in an accident,</i>

92
00:05:25,201 --> 00:05:28,120
<i>almost nobody will suspect me...</i>

93
00:05:28,830 --> 00:05:30,414
<i>Even if they do,
there's no evidence.</i>

94
00:05:31,541 --> 00:05:34,335
<i>I can only imagine
what will happen after L dies.</i>

95
00:05:35,127 --> 00:05:36,420
<i>This is all a wager now.</i>

96
00:05:38,172 --> 00:05:44,595
<i>Tomorrow will be L's...
no, Ryuzaki/Ryuga's final day.</i>

97
00:05:51,018 --> 00:05:52,019
Hair.

98
00:05:55,064 --> 00:05:56,440
Snack crumbs.

99
00:05:59,777 --> 00:06:00,778
Hair.

100
00:06:02,947 --> 00:06:03,948
Mr. Yagami.

101
00:06:05,241 --> 00:06:08,286
If I die within the next few days,
your son is Kira.

102
00:06:10,705 --> 00:06:11,706
Another hair.

103
00:06:13,958 --> 00:06:15,293
What did you just say?!

104
00:06:15,835 --> 00:06:17,837
Yeah. What are you
talking about?!

105
00:06:18,379 --> 00:06:21,048
I'll make sure that you
have ready access to Watari,

106
00:06:21,215 --> 00:06:22,800
I'm counting on you...

107
00:06:23,217 --> 00:06:24,218
Ryuzaki. . .!

108
00:06:24,760 --> 00:06:27,722
You said he was almost entirely cleared,
but I want the truth.

109
00:06:27,805 --> 00:06:29,765
How likely is it that he's-?!

110
00:06:30,391 --> 00:06:32,894
Even I don't know how I truly feel.

111
00:06:34,812 --> 00:06:36,731
This has never happened before...

112
00:06:37,648 --> 00:06:40,109
If Kira and the Second Kira
are working together...

113
00:06:40,192 --> 00:06:41,986
I'm in big trouble.

114
00:06:42,445 --> 00:06:47,825
So I might not be analyzing
the situation calmly...

115
00:06:51,329 --> 00:06:55,166
I might be considering him a suspect
just because there's nobody else...

116
00:06:55,625 --> 00:06:56,667
Despite that...

117
00:06:57,043 --> 00:07:01,339
If I'm killed now,
please assume that your son is Kira.

118
00:07:05,343 --> 00:07:07,094
<i>I have no choice
but to make a surprise attack.</i>

119
00:07:07,178 --> 00:07:08,179
<i>It can't be helped.</i>

120
00:07:08,846 --> 00:07:10,723
<i>This is all a wager now.</i>

121
00:07:24,195 --> 00:07:25,363
That's not true.

122
00:07:25,905 --> 00:07:27,531
I'm just good at
dealing with things...

123
00:07:33,746 --> 00:07:34,747
What's wrong?

124
00:07:38,709 --> 00:07:41,504
Oh, Yagami.

125
00:07:42,296 --> 00:07:43,297
Hello.

126
00:07:45,716 --> 00:07:49,095
Miss Takada,
I'd like to talk to him for moment.

127
00:07:49,178 --> 00:07:50,179
Could we continue this later?

128
00:07:50,346 --> 00:07:51,722
What? All right.

129
00:07:55,726 --> 00:07:57,353
Was that okay?

130
00:07:58,187 --> 00:07:59,230
More importantly,

131
00:07:59,313 --> 00:08:01,983
didn't you say that you were afraid
to appear in front of people?

132
00:08:02,066 --> 00:08:03,192
Are you all right out here?

133
00:08:03,401 --> 00:08:06,654
I realized that as long
as you're not Kira, it's okay.

134
00:08:07,613 --> 00:08:10,574
You're the only one on
the outside who knows I'm L...

135
00:08:11,575 --> 00:08:14,578
So, I've told everyone at headquarters
that if I die in the next few days...

136
00:08:15,329 --> 00:08:18,916
to assume that you're Kira.

137
00:08:20,918 --> 00:08:21,961
<i>Damn him...</i>

138
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:26,173
You told me that
you've been lonely

139
00:08:26,257 --> 00:08:28,509
because I've been taking
breaks from school,

140
00:08:29,260 --> 00:08:31,262
so I came out for a change of pace.

141
00:08:32,263 --> 00:08:34,306
As long as you don't die,
college is a fun place.

142
00:08:34,932 --> 00:08:36,851
Yeah. When you're not here,
it's so boring

143
00:08:36,934 --> 00:08:39,603
because there's no one who can
match my level of conversation.

144
00:08:40,104 --> 00:08:41,731
So that explains why
you're with the "brilliant" Takada.

145
00:08:42,314 --> 00:08:43,733
Well, something like that.

146
00:08:45,776 --> 00:08:48,946
<i>Should I really kill him today?</i>

147
00:08:49,780 --> 00:08:52,616
<i>No. . .As soon as I
decided to kill him,</i>

148
00:08:52,700 --> 00:08:55,953
<i>he suddenly appears, as if to
distract me from my resolution...</i>

149
00:08:56,370 --> 00:08:58,789
<i>to prevent me from killing him...</i>

150
00:08:59,832 --> 00:09:02,293
<i>This is exactly what he wants!</i>

151
00:09:03,711 --> 00:09:05,588
Shall we have some cake
in the cafeteria?

152
00:09:06,338 --> 00:09:08,883
Sure... My next lecture was cancelled.

153
00:09:09,341 --> 00:09:10,426
That's good.

154
00:09:12,011 --> 00:09:13,637
I wonder if they have shortcake?

155
00:09:14,305 --> 00:09:15,973
Well... who knows.

156
00:09:16,807 --> 00:09:18,893
Light! There you are!

157
00:09:20,019 --> 00:09:22,521
I came because I had
a photo shoot nearby!

158
00:09:22,897 --> 00:09:24,482
<i>Misa! You idiot!</i>

159
00:09:25,066 --> 00:09:26,484
Is this a friend of yours?

160
00:09:26,817 --> 00:09:28,527
He's so unique and cool...

161
00:09:29,945 --> 00:09:31,405
<i>No... I've won!</i>

162
00:09:32,281 --> 00:09:34,492
<i>Misa can see Ryuga's real name!</i>

163
00:09:35,493 --> 00:09:38,871
I'm Light's girlfriend, Misa Amane.
Pleased to meet you.

164
00:09:39,622 --> 00:09:40,664
I'm Hideki Ryuga.

165
00:09:41,957 --> 00:09:43,042
Huh? Hideki Ryuga?

166
00:09:44,126 --> 00:09:47,129
Yeah, he has the same first name
and last name as that idol.

167
00:09:47,797 --> 00:09:48,839
Isn't that funny?

168
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:52,218
<i>Buzj ifis cfifferenz' from
the name I'm seeing...</i>

169
00:09:53,052 --> 00:09:57,181
<i>Ryuga, coming outside like this
was a big mistake!</i>

170
00:10:01,852 --> 00:10:06,023
<i>Why's he laughing?
Does this mean he noticed?</i>

171
00:10:07,024 --> 00:10:09,485
<i>But if he's guessed that
she's the Second Kira,</i>

172
00:10:09,777 --> 00:10:11,570
<i>there's no way
he would be laughing...</i>

173
00:10:12,988 --> 00:10:13,989
Yagami...

174
00:10:16,367 --> 00:10:17,701
I'm jealous.

175
00:10:19,370 --> 00:10:22,206
I've been a huge fan of yours
since the August issue of "Eighteen."

176
00:10:22,540 --> 00:10:24,792
What? Really? I'm so happy...

177
00:10:25,000 --> 00:10:27,002
Hey, that girl.
Isn't she Misa-Misa?!

178
00:10:27,294 --> 00:10:29,296
It's true. It's Misa-Misa!

179
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:30,756
- Misa-Misa?!
- The real one?!

180
00:10:31,048 --> 00:10:32,341
I should have guessed
that I'd be discovered

181
00:10:32,424 --> 00:10:33,467
if there were
a lot of young people around.

182
00:10:33,801 --> 00:10:35,052
I look forward to
seeing you every month.

183
00:10:35,469 --> 00:10:36,720
Keep up the good work.

184
00:10:36,804 --> 00:10:39,056
Yeah. Thank you.
I'll do my best...

185
00:10:39,849 --> 00:10:40,891
<i>What's going on?</i>

186
00:10:41,267 --> 00:10:43,310
Hey! Who touched my butt?!

187
00:10:45,896 --> 00:10:47,314
How disgraceful!

188
00:10:47,398 --> 00:10:49,733
I won't forgive anyone who would
take advantage of this situation.

189
00:10:50,651 --> 00:10:52,111
I'll find the culprit.

190
00:10:53,988 --> 00:10:55,739
Ryuga! You're so funny!

191
00:10:56,448 --> 00:10:58,159
- I want to touch her, too.
- Stupid!

192
00:10:58,534 --> 00:11:01,787
<i>At any rate, I want to ask Misa what
L's name is as soon as possible,</i>

193
00:11:02,538 --> 00:11:04,081
<i>but these people are in the way.</i>

194
00:11:04,748 --> 00:11:05,749
Misa!

195
00:11:06,584 --> 00:11:07,668
It's time!

196
00:11:07,835 --> 00:11:09,086
Are you planning on
being late again?!

197
00:11:09,795 --> 00:11:11,046
Oh, sorry, Yoshi...

198
00:11:11,463 --> 00:11:13,340
- Let's g0!
- Oh, yeah!

199
00:11:14,383 --> 00:11:15,509
<i>Good...</i>

200
00:11:15,593 --> 00:11:17,178
<i>Once Misa's out of here,</i>

201
00:11:17,511 --> 00:11:20,014
<i>I just have to give her a call
and ask her for L's name.</i>

202
00:11:20,681 --> 00:11:24,018
See you after work, Light...

203
00:11:29,815 --> 00:11:32,026
Now then, shall we go, Yagami?

204
00:11:32,443 --> 00:11:33,444
Yeah...

205
00:11:33,944 --> 00:11:36,864
Sorry, could you go on ahead?
I need to go to the restroom.

206
00:11:37,573 --> 00:11:39,283
I see. See you there...

207
00:11:53,464 --> 00:11:54,506
<i>It's over...</i>

208
00:11:55,925 --> 00:11:58,510
<i>It's been fun... L.</i>

209
00:12:01,639 --> 00:12:05,935
<i>I'm glad that I could discover
your name and kill you myself.</i>

210
00:12:18,322 --> 00:12:20,491
<i>It's been fun L.</i>

211
00:12:21,283 --> 00:12:24,662
<i>I'm glad that I could discover
your name and kill you myself.</i>

212
00:12:54,525 --> 00:12:56,110
Yes, hello?

213
00:12:57,695 --> 00:12:58,946
What do you mean, "Hello"?

214
00:12:59,863 --> 00:13:02,324
Oh, this cell phone must have
been dropped

215
00:13:02,408 --> 00:13:04,535
by someone in
that commotion earlier.

216
00:13:05,077 --> 00:13:07,454
<i>Bastard. . .he must have...
back then...</i>

217
00:13:11,834 --> 00:13:12,960
Hello?

218
00:13:13,294 --> 00:13:15,713
<i>Yeah... That's Misa's cell phone, so...</i>

219
00:13:15,879 --> 00:13:17,256
I'll give it back to her.

220
00:13:18,173 --> 00:13:20,134
I see. I understand.

221
00:13:25,723 --> 00:13:31,895
<i>Ryuga probably thinks he's won,
but Misa has another phone.</i>

222
00:13:32,479 --> 00:13:33,731
<i>If I call that one...</i>

223
00:13:34,690 --> 00:13:37,776
Oh, this time...
it's my cell phone.

224
00:13:39,528 --> 00:13:40,571
Yes?

225
00:13:42,781 --> 00:13:45,034
Yes. I see. We did it.

226
00:13:46,410 --> 00:13:47,453
I understand.

227
00:13:49,788 --> 00:13:54,001
This may come as good and
bad news to you, but...

228
00:13:54,793 --> 00:13:56,795
Misa Amane has just been
taken into custody

229
00:13:56,879 --> 00:13:58,088
under suspicion
of being the Second Kira.

230
00:14:00,924 --> 00:14:02,760
<i>When in the world
did he find out about Misa?!</i>

231
00:14:03,844 --> 00:14:05,596
<i>I never thought he'd
catch her this quickly...</i>

232
00:14:06,805 --> 00:14:10,642
There were hairs and fibers,
among other things,

233
00:14:11,435 --> 00:14:14,188
attached to the masking tape
sealing the tapes the Second Kira sent.

234
00:14:14,271 --> 00:14:17,316
We discovered many matching samples
of evidence in her room.

235
00:14:18,692 --> 00:14:22,112
There will probably be a riot if
we charge her with being the Second Kira,

236
00:14:22,196 --> 00:14:24,156
so we're telling the public that
she's voluntarily coming with us

237
00:14:24,239 --> 00:14:26,408
because her manager is
suspected of drug possession.

238
00:14:27,284 --> 00:14:29,036
The truth will probably
never go public...

239
00:14:32,873 --> 00:14:33,874
<i>I was careless...</i>

240
00:14:34,375 --> 00:14:38,629
<i>That video. I should have
destroyed all the evidence...</i>

241
00:14:39,505 --> 00:14:41,965
<i>In the end,
Ryuga chose to protect himself</i>

242
00:14:42,091 --> 00:14:44,385
<i>by being with me instead of hiding.</i>

243
00:14:44,468 --> 00:14:46,136
<i>He confronted
the heart of the matter...</i>

244
00:14:48,931 --> 00:14:50,641
<i>This wager. . .is my...</i>

245
00:14:51,475 --> 00:14:52,559
<i>M)”...</i>

246
00:14:53,310 --> 00:14:54,395
<i>M)”...</i>

247
00:14:55,312 --> 00:14:56,313
<i>No!</i>

248
00:14:58,399 --> 00:14:59,525
<i>Not yet...</i>

249
00:15:00,818 --> 00:15:03,654
<i>The challenge is just beginning, L...</i>

250
00:15:12,996 --> 00:15:15,124
Watari, has she said anything?

251
00:15:15,499 --> 00:15:17,209
<i>No, she hasn't said anything yet.</i>

252
00:15:17,918 --> 00:15:19,586
Get me a visual of her.

253
00:15:20,045 --> 00:15:21,130
<i>Are you sure?</i>

254
00:15:21,213 --> 00:15:22,297
Yes, quickly.

255
00:15:30,848 --> 00:15:31,974
R-Ryuzaki!

256
00:15:32,391 --> 00:15:33,392
What's the meaning of this?!

257
00:15:34,309 --> 00:15:36,478
I've apprehended her
as the Second Kira.

258
00:15:36,645 --> 00:15:38,230
This, at the very least,
is necessary.

259
00:15:39,565 --> 00:15:41,608
Indeed, there was enough evidence
in Amane's room...

260
00:15:41,692 --> 00:15:44,778
to mark her as
the Second Kira, but...

261
00:15:45,904 --> 00:15:47,698
Yes. There's no mistake.

262
00:15:48,157 --> 00:15:50,075
Now all we have to do is
make her tell us how she kills...

263
00:15:50,284 --> 00:15:55,164
Whether she knows Kira,
and if she knows who he is.

264
00:15:56,039 --> 00:15:58,375
Watari. Take the proper precautions,

265
00:15:58,542 --> 00:16:00,919
but do whatever needs to be done,
I don't care what,

266
00:16:01,211 --> 00:16:02,421
to get her to confess.

267
00:16:02,629 --> 00:16:03,714
<i>Yes.</i>

268
00:16:04,131 --> 00:16:05,215
Also, Mr. Yagami...

269
00:16:06,425 --> 00:16:08,719
I'm probably going to
call Light in...

270
00:16:08,802 --> 00:16:10,679
as a prime suspect.

271
00:16:11,305 --> 00:16:12,514
Please be prepared for that.

272
00:16:33,410 --> 00:16:35,579
<i>Ryuzaki, Amane's talking.</i>

273
00:16:36,580 --> 00:16:38,499
Give me visuals...and sound quickly!

274
00:16:41,126 --> 00:16:42,920
Finally after three days, huh?!

275
00:16:45,339 --> 00:16:47,216
<i>I can't take it any more...</i>

276
00:16:49,843 --> 00:16:50,886
/(I'll me-

277
00:16:52,429 --> 00:16:54,765
<i>Kill me... Hurry up and kill me!</i>

278
00:16:55,807 --> 00:16:58,852
I guess it was too much
for a young girl...

279
00:16:59,811 --> 00:17:01,563
She must be at her limit...

280
00:17:02,898 --> 00:17:04,900
<i>Misa Amane, can you hear me?</i>

281
00:17:06,151 --> 00:17:10,197
I can hear you...
Please kill me now...

282
00:17:11,156 --> 00:17:14,660
Is this because you admit
to being the Second Kira?

283
00:17:15,118 --> 00:17:17,621
<i>No! I don't know anything
about the Second Kira!</i>

284
00:17:18,622 --> 00:17:22,751
I can't take this anymore. . .!
I'd rather die...

285
00:17:24,169 --> 00:17:25,796
Just hurry up and kill me!

286
00:17:26,505 --> 00:17:28,882
You should be able to
kill me immediately, right?!

287
00:17:31,593 --> 00:17:33,595
Misa. . .do you mean-?

288
00:17:33,929 --> 00:17:35,639
Yes, kill me.

289
00:17:36,473 --> 00:17:38,392
You want me to kill you?

290
00:17:38,642 --> 00:17:40,394
Yes... Kill me...

291
00:17:42,896 --> 00:17:45,566
I can't take it anymore... Kill me...

292
00:17:46,775 --> 00:17:49,486
If I kill you, I'll kill Light Yagami.

293
00:17:50,153 --> 00:17:51,363
This all happened because of him.

294
00:17:51,822 --> 00:17:55,242
No! No...
Kill me...

295
00:17:55,742 --> 00:17:59,288
Misa. .. You want so badly...
to die for h/nv?

296
00:18:01,373 --> 00:18:03,917
That's it! If you won't kill me...!

297
00:18:04,001 --> 00:18:06,044
This is not good, Watari...
Don't let her bite her tongue!

298
00:18:13,677 --> 00:18:15,929
Could it be that these are
just actions

299
00:18:16,013 --> 00:18:18,015
controlled by Kira before death?

300
00:18:19,641 --> 00:18:20,892
Oh Rem.

301
00:18:21,018 --> 00:18:22,477
What's this all of a sudden?

302
00:18:25,063 --> 00:18:26,231
Light Yagami...

303
00:18:27,190 --> 00:18:30,277
I offered to help Misa escape,
but she refused.

304
00:18:30,944 --> 00:18:33,989
She probably thought it would
get you in trouble

305
00:18:34,239 --> 00:18:36,950
since the police think that
she has special powers...

306
00:18:38,452 --> 00:18:41,288
And when she was
at her wit's end,

307
00:18:41,371 --> 00:18:44,166
she started asking me to kill her.

308
00:18:46,084 --> 00:18:48,545
This is all because
she wants you to love her.

309
00:18:51,506 --> 00:18:54,468
No matter how much she asked,
I couldn't kill her...

310
00:18:55,177 --> 00:18:56,386
I couldn't bear watching her...

311
00:18:57,888 --> 00:19:00,682
There was only one way
to save her from that suffering.

312
00:19:01,558 --> 00:19:04,061
Forfeiting ownership
of the Death Note.

313
00:19:04,770 --> 00:19:05,812
That's right.

314
00:19:06,396 --> 00:19:08,732
If she forfeits ownership
of the Death Note,

315
00:19:09,399 --> 00:19:12,361
all memories related to
the Death Note will disappear.

316
00:19:13,195 --> 00:19:15,405
All memories of murders
she committed with her notebook,

317
00:19:15,697 --> 00:19:19,159
and the fact that you are Kira,
will disappear.

318
00:19:19,701 --> 00:19:22,496
Misa will not reveal your secret.

319
00:19:23,997 --> 00:19:28,126
Also, Misa will no longer
be able to see Ryuk or me.

320
00:19:29,836 --> 00:19:32,422
SEVERAL HOURS EARLIER

321
00:19:32,589 --> 00:19:36,760
You will forget
everything about Shinigami.

322
00:19:39,554 --> 00:19:44,142
It's all right. The human
you love is Light Yagami.

323
00:19:44,935 --> 00:19:47,062
Those emotions will remain.

324
00:19:50,649 --> 00:19:54,653
So Misa, forfeit ownership
of the notebook

325
00:19:54,820 --> 00:19:57,155
and leave everything to Light Yagami.

326
00:20:29,938 --> 00:20:33,066
Misa no longer owns the Death Note.

327
00:20:33,859 --> 00:20:35,402
You did well, Rem...

328
00:20:36,069 --> 00:20:38,864
I was beginning to think
that was the only way.

329
00:20:39,656 --> 00:20:41,616
If her memories of
the Death Note are erased,

330
00:20:41,825 --> 00:20:44,327
then it's not impossible
to get Misa released.

331
00:20:45,412 --> 00:20:48,373
Light Yagami, I proposed this
to Misa

332
00:20:48,457 --> 00:20:54,004
because I knew this is the method
you would have desired the most.

333
00:20:55,756 --> 00:20:59,259
If you don't save Misa, I'll kill you.

334
00:21:08,143 --> 00:21:09,394
I understand, Rem.

335
00:21:10,228 --> 00:21:12,689
I think I have a good idea
of what L is going to do next.

336
00:21:13,774 --> 00:21:15,066
I have a plan.

337
00:21:18,278 --> 00:21:19,696
This is good bye, Ryuk.

338
00:21:20,781 --> 00:21:21,865
What?

339
00:21:22,115 --> 00:21:25,535
TO BE CONTINUED

340
00:21:25,869 --> 00:21:30,916
<i>I dreamed a dream
that no one could see,</i>

341
00:21:30,999 --> 00:21:36,338
<i>I threw away everything
that I didn't need</i>

342
00:21:36,421 --> 00:21:38,799
<i>I'm holding these feelings</i>

343
00:21:38,882 --> 00:21:45,347
<i>That I can't give up in my heart</i>

344
00:21:45,472 --> 00:21:51,728
<i>Even if my feet fall victim
to the shackles of sacrifice</i>

345
00:21:51,812 --> 00:21:56,316
<i>In between reality and my ideal</i>

346
00:21:57,108 --> 00:22:01,988
<i>I can't hold back
the flooding impulses</i>

347
00:22:02,072 --> 00:22:04,866
<i>Because I have a strong desire</i>

348
00:22:04,950 --> 00:22:09,454
<i>To accomplish</i>

349
00:22:10,038 --> 00:22:14,668
<i>[deceit] [fear] [vanity] [melancholy]</i>

350
00:22:14,751 --> 00:22:19,297
<i>I'm not weak enough to believe</i>

351
00:22:19,381 --> 00:22:25,387
<i>Any of these negative perceptions</i>

352
00:22:25,887 --> 00:22:31,226
<i>I'm a trickster
who doesn't know solitude</i>

353
00:22:35,480 --> 00:22:37,148
PREVIEW

354
00:22:37,607 --> 00:22:42,362
Yeah... I know I probably look
pretty bad in here...

355
00:22:43,029 --> 00:22:45,448
but this pride...
I'll just have to...

356
00:22:46,616 --> 00:22:47,701
get rid of it!

357
00:22:47,909 --> 00:22:50,495
NEXT EPISODE: DECISION

